<div class="about-me-box about-me-expedient">
    <div class="container">
        <p>
            <h2>I am currently working as a software applications engineer for Expedient, a cloud infrastructure and managed services company.</h2>
            <img class="osu-logo" src="/images/aboutme/expedient_logo.jpg">
            <br>
            <p class="body-text">
                I currently work with a small team to build, deliver and maintain distributed software applications that support the cloud and managed service business. 
                Our applications are written in PHP and Go. I have also developed CI pipelines with github actions that build, test and deploy our applications.
                Continuous deployment to our kubernetes clusters is handled by ArgoCD.
            </p>
        </p>
