<div class="about-me-box about-me-osu">
    <div class="container">
        <p>
            <h2>I have a bachelors degree in computer science from Oregon State University.</h2>
            <img class="osu-logo" src="/images/aboutme/osu3.png">
            <br>
            <p class="body-text">
                I became interested in computer science while talking to one of my co-workers while in training at Piedmont Airlines.
                Seeing some of the projects he and other acquaintances were working on inspired me to start studying it for myself.
                I started Harvard's online 
                <a href="https://www.edx.org/course/introduction-computer-science-harvardx-cs50x" target="_blank">CS50 course</a>
                and got about halfway through before deciding I wanted to learn as much as I could about computer science. I enrolled 
                in OSU's completely online post-bacc program soon after and in December 2018 I graduated from the program. 
            </p>
        </p>
    </div>
